title: Sik Fan Lah
overview: When it's time to eat, we say SIK FAN LAH! Take a culinary adventure across Aotearoa New Zealand, uncovering hilarious and hearty stories of modern Kiwi-Chinese life through our universal love for food. Made with the support of NZ On Air.Featuring Masterchef 2022 and barista champ Sam Low, Olympic Gold medallist Tyla-Nathan Wong, and many more from the Kiwi-Chinese community - this series will give you plenty to munch on.Â
